<div class="heroBanner">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="freeBadge">✦ 100% FREE — Open Source Book</div>
    <h1 class="hero__title">Ship It</h1>
    <p class="hero__subtitle">By developers, for developers — From first idea to first user, no MBA required.</p>
    <p class="heroWarning">🚨 90% of side projects never launch. 70% of startups fail from no market need. 85% of developers never ship a personal product. This book shows you how to find problems, validate ideas, and build products that people actually use. <strong>Start reading now — it's free.</strong></p>
    <div class="heroCtaRow">
      <a href="/introduction/" class="ctaButton">Start Reading — The Introduction →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="homepageSection">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="sectionTitle">8 Parts. One Mission: Your Startup.</h2>
    <div class="partsGrid">
      <a href="/introduction/" class="partCard">
        <div class="partCardIcon">📖</div>
        <h3>Introduction — The Builder Reality Check</h3>
        <p>5 chapters. Why you haven't built anything yet, the product gap, the startup myth, and how this book changes everything.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/part-1-builder-mindset/" class="partCard">
        <div class="partCardIcon">🧠</div>
        <h3>Part 1: The Builder Mindset</h3>
        <p>2 chapters. Rewire how you think about building. Break the tutorial trap and perfectionism cycle.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/part-2-find-the-problem/" class="partCard">
        <div class="partCardIcon">🔍</div>
        <h3>Part 2: Find &amp; Validate the Problem</h3>
        <p>4 chapters. Identify yourself as a builder, read markets, think problem-first, and validate before building.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/part-3-design-the-solution/" class="partCard">
        <div class="partCardIcon">🏗️</div>
        <h3>Part 3: Design the Solution</h3>
        <p>3 chapters. Think in systems, research your domain, and design before you write a single line of code.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/part-4-build-it/" class="partCard">
        <div class="partCardIcon">⚒️</div>
        <h3>Part 4: Build It</h3>
        <p>3 chapters. Build an MVP, make smart stack decisions, and debug like a thinker, not a guesser.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/part-5-deploy-and-show/" class="partCard">
        <div class="partCardIcon">🚀</div>
        <h3>Part 5: Deploy &amp; Show</h3>
        <p>3 chapters. Ship your first version, get your first real user, and launch on channels that work.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/part-6-listen-and-iterate/" class="partCard">
        <div class="partCardIcon">🔄</div>
        <h3>Part 6: Listen &amp; Iterate</h3>
        <p>3 chapters. Collect real feedback, know when to pivot, and iterate without breaking things.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/part-7-build-in-public/" class="partCard">
        <div class="partCardIcon">🌍</div>
        <h3>Part 7: Build in Public</h3>
        <p>4 chapters. Build on GitHub, grow on Twitter/LinkedIn, find your community, and play the long game.</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

